---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact — AIBolt Labs" description="Project support and public contact paths for AIBolt Labs.">
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="shell"><div class="eyebrow">Contact</div><h1 class="page-title">Keep the conversation<br />close to the work.</h1><p class="lead">Public project questions are most useful when they remain searchable, reproducible, and attached to the source they concern.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="shell grid-3">
    <article class="card"><span class="number">BUGS</span><h2>Report an issue</h2><p>Use the DYNT issue tracker for reproducible defects, unexpected browser behaviour, or documentation gaps.</p><a class="card-link" href="https://github.com/aibolt/dynt/issues">Open issues ↗</a></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="number">SOURCE</span><h2>Propose a change</h2><p>Read the contribution guidance before opening a pull request. Maintainers review changes against the project contracts.</p><a class="card-link" href="https://github.com/aibolt/dynt/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">Contribution guide ↗</a></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="number">MEDIA</span><h2>Follow demonstrations</h2><p>Project walkthroughs and future release demonstrations are published through the AIBolt Labs channel.</p><a class="card-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/@AiBoltLabs">YouTube channel ↗</a></article>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
